{"type":null,"faqId":14370,"title":"What do I do with my wrist to turn on my B1's screen?","answer":"<p>\n<span><span>Your B1 has unique motion operations. You can turn on your B1's screen as follows:</span></span>\n</p>\n<p>\n<span><span><span>1.</span><span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><span><span>Wear your B1 on your wrist and raise your wrist levelly.</span></span>\n</p>\n<p>\n<span><span><span>2.</span><span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><span><span>Rotate your wrist outwards for 90 degrees and turn it back. Then you can see the screen is on.</span></span>\n</p>\n<p>\n<span><span><span>3.</span><span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><span><span>Rotate your wrist again to switch between screens.</span></span>\n</p>\n<p align=\"center\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=47359\">\n</p>\n<p>\n&nbsp;\n</p>","faqTypeId":334,"faqType":"Screen Display","useful":13,"unUseful":3,"languageId":1,"languageName":"en","faqCode":"6332","faqTypeCode":"Wearable_Device-Screen-Display","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1408439405000,"seriesProductName":"B1","visitedTimes":934,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}